%h1 Listing comments

%table
  %tr
    %th Body
    %th Character proxy
    %th User profile
    %th Commentable
    %th Commentable type
    %th Has been deleted
    %th Has been edited
    %th Has been locked
    %th Community
    %th
    %th
    %th

  - @comments.each do |comment|
    %tr
      %td= comment.body
      %td= comment.character_proxy_id
      %td= comment.user_profile_id
      %td= comment.commentable_id
      %td= comment.commentable_type
      %td= comment.has_been_deleted
      %td= comment.has_been_edited
      %td= comment.has_been_locked
      %td= comment.community_id
      %td= link_to 'Show', comment
      %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_comment_path(comment)
      %td= link_to 'Destroy', comment, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete

